metadata.name: Superluminal #78 v2 animated
metadata.description: Superluminal is a series of abstract paintings made up of acrylics, inks, fluid paint and glitter. In astronomy superluminal motion is travelling faster than the speed of light. This series aims to create an energy and vibrancy that alludes to another world. Then taken to the next level as animated fluid art with flowing elements, creating beautiful shapes and motion.
